The wheel was mounted on a mast, but in the same year it had to be brought down.
The manufacturer of the replica did not choose the right material and the wheel could not resist the gusts of wind.
Then the Chlum dominant rested under the roof for several years.
However, since June this year, the high-mast wheel has been spinning again.
