The European Union must work to improve humanitarian conditions in refugee camps in Jordan and Lebanon in order to limit the flow of refugees into Europe.
This was announced by German Chancellor Angela Merkel after talks with German prime ministers.
At the same time, she again called for the distribution of refugees who have already arrived in the EU among the 28 member states.
